# Đề bài

Cho $\left|\overrightarrow{a}\right|=2$, $\left|\overrightarrow{b}\right|=3$, $\left|\overrightarrow{a}+2\overrightarrow{b}\right|=5$. Tìm $\left|3\overrightarrow{a}-\overrightarrow{b}\right\|$.

A. $135$

B. $11$

C. $\dfrac{3 \sqrt{30}}{2}$

D. $45$

# Lời giải

Ta có $\left|\overrightarrow{a}+2\overrightarrow{b}\right|^2=\left(\overrightarrow{a}+2\overrightarrow{b}\right)^2=\overrightarrow{a}^2+4\overrightarrow{a}\overrightarrow{b}+4\overrightarrow{b}^2=\left|\overrightarrow{a}\right|^2+4\overrightarrow{a}\overrightarrow{b}+4\left|\overrightarrow{b}\right|^2$. 

Suy ra 
$$
\overrightarrow{a}\overrightarrow{b}=\dfrac{1}{4}\left(\left|\overrightarrow{a}+2\overrightarrow{b}\right|^2-\left|\overrightarrow{a}\right|^2-4\left|\overrightarrow{b}\right|^2\right)=\dfrac{1}{4}\left(5^2-2^2-4\cdot 3^2\right)=-\dfrac{15}{4}.
$$ 
Khi đó, 
$$
\left|3\overrightarrow{a}-\overrightarrow{b}\right|^2=\left(3\overrightarrow{a}-\overrightarrow{b}\right)^2=9\overrightarrow{a}^2-6\overrightarrow{a}\overrightarrow{b}+\overrightarrow{b}^2=9\left|\overrightarrow{a}\right|^2-6\overrightarrow{a}\overrightarrow{b}+\left|\overrightarrow{b}\right|^2=9\cdot 2^2+\dfrac{45}{2}+3^2=\dfrac{135}{2}.
$$
Vậy $\left|3\overrightarrow{a}-\overrightarrow{b}\right|=\dfrac{3\sqrt{30}}{2}$.

